feed.title: LIU Yinuo
feed.subtitle: Hello, I'm Yinuo Liu (also call me Nicole Liu). I'm in my third year studying psychology at Zhejiang University, China. I've also learned courses in various academic fields include psycholinguistics, neuroscience, machine learning, artificial intelligence, data analysis and so on. My personal research interests focus on language and working memory, and I have posted one of my research in OHBM 2022 Annual Meeting.
